<anchor id="filter_8h_1filter"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>Zero phase filtering inmplementation based on Python and Matlab filtfilt function. The base of this c++ implementation is <ulink url="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/17675053/matlabs-filtfilt-algorithm/27270420#27270420">Implementation of Darien Pardinas</ulink>. Eigen library is replaced by matrix operations. The filtfilt algorithm matches the initial conditions on the filter to minimise start and end transients.</para>
</simplesect>
